Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:15.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}本当に現実なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:20.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}心がまだ追いついて来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}今は想像出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:28.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}この先押し寄せる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:32.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}Still,I have to keep going this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:34.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}あなたが居ない世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:36.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}miss you so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:40.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}消えないこの鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:43.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}会いたいあの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:49.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}もう一度近づきたい話したい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}I know life can be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:59.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}最後の言葉をねぇちゃんと聞かせてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:03.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}I wish you would stay with me.
