Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:11.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}I can not live without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:16.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}あなたに捧げよう
