Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.07,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}眼下还无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:28.31,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}这奔涌而来的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:32.13,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我依旧要在这世间前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:34.61,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}在这没有了你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:36.34,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我是如此想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:40.05,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}这永不消弭的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:43.96,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}多想再见到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:49.25,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}想再一次贴近你 与你欢谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.17,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我已知晓 生命竟能如此煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:59.45,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}你最后的话语 我多么想要听到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:03.48,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}只愿你能与我相伴
